elements.name: beneficiaryFICode

elements.name: beneficiaryCode
elements.desc: mandatory if 3600.businessFunctionCode is in (CTR,CTP,DRW or DRC); mandatory if 4200.beneficiaryIdentifier is present; If 4200.beneficiaryCode = T then 3600.businessFunctionCode must be (CTP, CTR)

elements.name: beneficiaryIdentifier
elements.desc: mandatory if 4200.beneficiaryCode is present; If 4200.beneficiaryCode IN (B,F,U) then 4200.beneficiaryIdentifier will be edited for proper structure; If 4200.beneficiaryCode = T then 4200.beneficiaryIdentifier must be present and contain an account number

elements.name: beneficiaryName
elements.desc: If 4200.beneficiaryCode = T then 4200.beneficiaryName must be present and contain a SWIFT BIC or BEI, which will be edited for proper structure

elements.name: accountDebitedCode

elements.name: accountDebitedIdentifier

elements.name: accountDebitedName

elements.name: originatorCode

elements.name: originatorName
